I'm gonna grow dozens of bacteria samples

01:18.078 --> 01:21.623
while my classmates are out
livin' it up on a three-day weekend.

01:21.707 --> 01:24.042
It's not fair. I need a brain break.

01:25.627 --> 01:27.921
Cool surfboard, Marshall.

01:29.631 --> 01:31.049
There it is.

01:32.885 --> 01:35.554
Just let me feel sorry for myself
for a second.

01:36.346 --> 01:38.265
What has gotten into you, Sprockie?

01:39.183 --> 01:41.977
What is it? You know what?

01:42.060 --> 01:45.022
That is a good idea, Sprockie.
We could go on vacation right here.

01:45.105 --> 01:47.107
It'll just take some imagination.

01:47.191 --> 01:49.484
But, unlike money,
we've got plenty of that.

01:49.568 --> 01:51.069
Thanks, Sprockie. I needed that.

01:57.743 --> 02:01.663
Well, I tell ya. It was a close call
getting my Uncle Matt's package today.

02:02.539 --> 02:04.708
But it looks to be
a pretty special dispatch.

02:04.791 --> 02:08.628
Yeah, he's going on about
something called a "vacation."

02:11.215 --> 02:12.716
"Cave-ation."

02:12.799 --> 02:14.468
No, no, no. Vibration.

02:14.551 --> 02:17.721
-Well…
-"Waka-talka-tation"?

02:19.139 --> 02:21.391
What's a vacation?

02:21.475 --> 02:23.727
-Well, Red, a vaca--
-Yeah.

02:23.810 --> 02:25.395
-You see, it's…
-Yeah?

02:25.479 --> 02:26.563
Let's find out.

02:27.481 --> 02:29.066
"Dear Nephew Gobo,

02:29.149 --> 02:32.736
Exploring can be draining,
and I was looking for a way to relax."

02:32.819 --> 02:35.030
That's when I discovered
something called…

02:35.113 --> 02:36.198
A vacation.

02:36.281 --> 02:38.992
It's where all the Silly Creatures
go to relax.

02:39.076 --> 02:42.204
They love it.
Why else would they come here every day?

02:42.287 --> 02:43.288
Hello!

02:43.372 --> 02:44.998
Hi.

02:45.082 --> 02:47.543
