you're looking for,

02:47.626 --> 02:48.877
they've got you covered.

02:48.961 --> 02:50.671
All yours. The water's great.

02:53.382 --> 02:55.926
They even had a light massage cavern.

02:56.009 --> 02:59.388
I could feel the stress melting away
from my bendy parts.

03:00.848 --> 03:02.474
Five more minutes, please.

03:08.939 --> 03:12.693
After a long day of relaxing,
I had developed quite a thirst.

03:16.446 --> 03:17.906
I developed quite a thirst.

03:27.291 --> 03:28.292
What?

03:28.375 --> 03:32.212
