03:46.185 --> 03:48.687
Wow. So that's what a vacation is.

03:48.770 --> 03:49.771
Yeah!

03:49.855 --> 03:54.818
Relaxation, water.
Sounds like what we do all the time.

03:54.902 --> 03:56.111
Yeah, Wembley.

03:56.195 --> 04:00.282
