in a different place.

04:00.365 --> 04:02.993
-Yep.
-I want to go on a vacation.

04:03.076 --> 04:04.161
-Yeah.
-Yeah.

04:06.079 --> 04:07.998
Well, vacation's gonna have to wait.

04:08.081 --> 04:10.250
