ahead of us.

04:10.334 --> 04:13.045
-Yeah, let's go, everyone. Come on.
-All right.

04:13.128 --> 04:16.964
-We'll see you there, Wembley.
-Okay. Just gotta put on my fire hat.

04:17.048 --> 04:18.634
Hello, dear friend.

04:21.470 --> 04:22.971
Hey, Cotterpin.

04:23.055 --> 04:27.768
Is this the sticky goo we found coming up
out of those vines a while back?

04:27.851 --> 04:32.523
When can we start building with it?
Today? Tomorrow? Today?

04:32.606 --> 04:35.275
Whoa, slow down there, Turbo.

04:35.359 --> 04:37.236
We need to do more tests.

04:37.319 --> 04:40.781
What if it doesn't hold
or tastes bad to the Fraggles?

04:41.281 --> 04:42.449
Not to mention--

04:42.533 --> 04:45.953
Bop, bop, bop!
Come on, you're worried about nothing.

04:46.036 --> 04:49.081
You deserve recognition
for this discovery.

04:49.164 --> 04:50.499
Yeah!

04:50.582 --> 04:56.213
It's not about praise.
It's about teamwork and sticking together.

04:56.296 --> 04:59.466
Yeah, this goo helps us stick together.

04:59.550 --> 05:02.886
We know that's not what you meant.
We messed up.

05:02.970 --> 05:05.389
We're goofballs!

05:13.230 --> 05:14.439
Workweek over!

05:14.940 --> 05:16.900
Thank goodness.

05:16.984 --> 05:19.611
I thought that workweek
would never be over.

05:19.695 --> 05:20.696
Oh, yeah.

05:21.697 --> 05:24.032
To be fair, it was only 30 minutes.

05:24.116 --> 05:26.785
An exhausting 30 minutes.

05:26.869 --> 05:29.413
I had to blow
my lifeguard whistle and yell

05:29.496 --> 05:33.166
"Keep having fun"
to all the Fraggles in the pond.

05:33.250 --> 05:34.835
I'm beat.

05:34.918 --> 05:37.171
Well, I feel rejuvenated.

05:37.254 --> 05:41.967
Picking radishes out of the Gorgs' garden,
connecting to the bounty of the harvest.

05:42.050 --> 05:43.343
Oh, I love my work.

05:43.427 --> 05:46.805
Me too. Cleaning my Uncle Matt's
museum is an honor.

05:46.889 --> 05:49.516
And, boy, did I clean it.
It was already clean,

05:49.600 --> 05:52.186
