-Cool!

05:54.563 --> 05:58.400
Well, I got to sound the alarm and help
the bucket brigade put out a fire.

05:59.568 --> 06:02.237
It wasn't a fire. It was my soup.

06:02.321 --> 06:03.780
A cold soup.

06:04.406 --> 06:06.700
-Sorry.
-Unbelievable.

06:06.783 --> 06:09.745
-Well, let's put the workweek behind us.
-Yeah.

06:09.828 --> 06:13.832
Because it's time to go
on a much-deserved vacation!

06:13.916 --> 06:15.626
All right!

06:15.709 --> 06:21.173
Hold on to your baloobiuses
because I know exactly where we should go!

06:21.965 --> 06:23.133
