What brings you to Craggle Lagoon?

10:48.315 --> 10:51.443
Hey, buddy.
I'm asking the questions around here.

10:51.527 --> 10:53.487
Now, who are you?

10:53.570 --> 10:55.155
I'm Lyle. I just said that.

10:56.073 --> 10:58.408
I'm a Craggle. And this is our lagoon.

10:58.492 --> 11:00.285
At least it was until it all dried up.

11:01.912 --> 11:03.747
We're the Craggles. We live here.

11:03.830 --> 11:04.998
More suspects!

11:05.832 --> 11:07.501
